### Component Patterns

**Primary Button:**
- Background: Green gradient (`#059669` to `#047857`)
- Text: White, medium weight
- Radius: 8px (lg)
- Shadow: medium elevation
- Press: scale to 0.98

**Secondary Button:**
- Background: Transparent
- Border: 1px green
- Text: Green
- Press: scale to 0.98

**Cards:**
- Background: White (or `background.secondary`)
- Border: 1px `border.subtle`
- Radius: 6px (md)
- Shadow: low elevation

**Feature Cards (with color):**
- Left accent bar: 4px colored
- Icon container: 44x44px, colored background at 15% opacity
- Icon: 24px, matching color

**Quick Action Cards:**
- Icon container: 40x40px, colored background at 20% opacity
- Label: caption style, secondary text color

**Inputs:**
- Background: `background.primary`
- Border: 1px `border.default`
- Radius: 4px (sm)
- Height: 40px
- Focus: Green border

**Selection States:**
- Background: `{color}10` (10% opacity tint)
- Border: 1px colored
- Checkmark: White on colored circle

### Animation Timing

| Token | Duration | Usage |
