**Easing:** ease-out for all transitions

### Navigation

**Tab Bar:**
- Background: White with 1px top border
- Active: Green icon + text
- Inactive: Tertiary gray
- FAB: Green gradient, 56px, centered

**Headers:**
- Background: White with 1px bottom border
- Title: h4 style, primary text
- No shadow (hairline border only)

### Icon Usage

- Use MaterialIcons from `@expo/vector-icons`
- Default size: 22px (md)
- Color: Match text hierarchy or use accent colors
- Always pair with tinted background container for emphasis

### Gradients

**Primary CTA Gradient:**

```typescript
colors={[theme.colors.primary, theme.colors.primaryDark]}
start={{ x: 0, y: 0 }}
end={{ x: 1, y: 1 }}
```

**Hero Background Gradient:**

```typescript
colors={[`${theme.colors.primary}15`, `${theme.colors.primary}05`, 'transparent']}
```

### Do's and Don'ts

**Do:**
- Use green as the primary accent throughout
- Add colorful accents (blue, purple, amber) to differentiate features
- Use hairline borders with subtle shadows
- Include press animations on interactive elements
- Use icon containers with tinted backgrounds
- Keep touch targets at least 44px

**Don't:**
- Use solid colored card backgrounds (old 2010s pattern)
- Use heavy shadows without borders
- Use more than 2-3 colors per screen
- Skip the green accent for primary actions
- Use pure black text (use `#171717` instead)
- Forget dark mode support
